lenders.name: Friends of Kiva San Francisco
lenders.loan_because: Thanks to the generosity of Kiva's supporters who attended our Kiva San Francisco launch event on October 1, 2015, we are thrilled to match loans in San Francisco, empowering small businesses across our city.  For more information, please visit www.Kiva.org/SF.
